snippet.title: Boxed In
snippet.description:
Ready to try one of the best f'n puzzle games in the world?.. Boxed In is a logic based puzzle game in which you guide a box-pushing robot through each level towards the exit. Sound simple? It gets tough. Real tough!

Download Boxed In now FREE for iOS: https://apple.co/2vVZiKV
